/capability, scan front-left-right and store a mock FaceTemplateRef.','Batch 08 s\u1ebd l\xe0m th\u1ebb th\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ebb kh\xe1ch s\u1ea1n v\xe0 th\u1ebb offline theo policy.':'Batch 08 will cover normal cards, hotel cards and offline cards by policy.','V\u1ec1 Credential Hub':'Back to Credential Hub','Batch 09 s\u1ebd pair remote v\u1eadt l\xfd b\u1eb1ng serial/model/battery v\xe0 g\xe1n ph\u1ea1m vi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.':'Batch 09 will pair a physical remote by serial/model/battery and assign usage scope.','Batch 21 s\u1ebd l\xe0m booking calendar, check-in t\u1ea1o quy\u1ec1n, check-out thu h\u1ed3i, import v\xe0 self check-in cho kh\xe1ch.':'Batch 21 will cover booking calendar, check-in credential creation, check-out revoke, import and guest self check-in.','Batch 18 s\u1ebd x\xe1c minh Owner b\u1eb1ng OTP/App PIN, ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn accept trong th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\xe0 ghi audit \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7.':'Batch 18 will verify the Owner by OTP/App PIN, require recipient acceptance before expiry and write full audit logs.','Batch 19 s\u1ebd l\xe0m PIN+card, Face+PIN, Card+fingerprint theo kh\xf3a/ph\xf2ng/ng\u01b0\u1eddi/th\u1eddi gian.':'Batch 19 will cover PIN+card, Face+PIN and Card+fingerprint rules by lock/room/user/time.','Batch 19 s\u1ebd l\xe0m normally-open, l\u1ecbch l\u1edbp/l\u1ecbch ca, ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7 ng\xe0y ngh\u1ec9 v\xe0 ki\u1ec3m tra timezone.':'Batch 19 will cover normally-open, class/shift schedules, holiday exceptions and timezone checks.','Batch 25 s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb pending/success/fail jobs, retry/cancel v\xe0 conflict resolution.':'Batch 25 will show pending/success/fail jobs, retry/cancel and conflict resolution.','Batch 28 s\u1ebd l\xe0m support ticket, warranty info, maintenance task v\xe0 diagnostic package \u0111\xe3 redaction.':'Batch 28 will cover support tickets, warranty info, maintenance tasks and redacted diagnostic packages.','Mock ch\u1ecdn m\u1ea1ng Wi\u2011Fi, nh\u1eadp m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u v\x