edn hi\u1ec7u':'Signal','M\u1edf qu\xe1 l\xe2u':'Open too long','M\xe3 PIN':'PIN code','\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n v\u1eadt l\xfd':'Physical control','\u1ee6y quy\u1ec1n phone':'Phone authorization','UI-11/51 g\xe1n kh\xf3a':'UI-11/51 lock assignment','Remote unlock \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n':'Remote unlock is blocked','M\u1edf m\xe0n Remote Unlock \u0111\u1ec3 xem checklist quy\u1ec1n, setting, gateway v\xe0 tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i online.':'Open Remote Unlock to view the checklist for permissions, settings, gateway and online status.','T\xe1c v\u1ee5 nhanh':'Quick actions','Command & audit g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t':'Latest command & audit','Command v\xe0 m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u mock s\u1ebd ghi v\xe0o Records \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m th\u1eed audit.':'Commands and mock passwords are written to Records for audit testing.','Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3 success event':'Device returns success event','Gateway tr\u1ea3 l\u1ed7i mock':'Gateway returns mock error','Kh\xf3a l\u1ea1i qua Gateway':'Lock via Gateway','Remote unlock ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t checklist an to\xe0n. Vui l\xf2ng ki\u1ec3m tra quy\u1ec1n, gateway v\xe0 setting.':'Remote unlock has not passed the safety checklist. Please check permissions, gateway and settings.','Kh\xf4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c command. Ki\u1ec3m tra tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i online/quy\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n.':'Could not create command. Check online status/control permission.','X\xe1c th\u1ef1c remote unlock Aplus':'Authenticate Aplus remote unlock','Sinh tr\u1eafc h\u1ecdc mock th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.':'Mock biometrics failed.','UI-37 x\xe1c th\u1ef1c':'UI-37 authentication','Nh\u1eadp PIN \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1eeb xa':'Enter PIN for remote unlock','D\xf9ng PIN':'Use PIN','G\u1eedi l\u1ec7nh kh\xf3a l\u1ea1i':'Send lock command','Command ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i khi nh\u1eadn success event, timeout/failed gi\u1eef nguy\xean tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i kh\xf3a.':'Command state changes only after a success event; timeout/failed keeps th